{"tid":737738,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跟低價團遊港澳曾被迫購物　江蘇翁猝死強國火車上","createTime":"2018-07-11T04:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T07:44:11.000Z","uid":75969,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"73eae8b40df8480aee76ced59e0c2aee3a51f532","tid":737738,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T04:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180711/photo/bkn-20180711020011994-0711_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180711092044\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180711%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180711020011994-0711_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180711092044&h=bb674d6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n江蘇常州一名74歲的呂姓老翁早前和妻子及4名親友，以每位988元（人民幣．下同，約1186港元）的費用，參加了一個低價旅行團，9日內暢遊香港、澳門、廣州、深圳、桂林等8個城市。惟旅途期間，呂翁在火車上突然猝死。一名同行親友指，老翁曾向導遊表示身體不適，但仍然被要求強制購物，懷疑與此有關。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該團約30人，且以長者為主。呂翁的妻子透露，涉事旅行團4月13日抵達香港後，「一整天都是購物」，全天花了7個小時逛4間商店，幾乎沒有參觀任何景點；該團翌天抵達澳門後，導遊因他們未有購物態度變得不好，更表示要額外支付130元（約156港元），才可取消本應參加的一個購物活動。<br />\n<br />\n涉事旅行團其後於4月15日來到珠海一間購物店，且必須5小時後方可上車。期間呂翁兩度表示身體不適，不想下車，惟導遊不同意。翌日，呂翁在廣州至桂林的火車上突然昏迷倒下，由於車上醫療條件有限，唯有等到下車處理，最終經送院搶救後不治。<br />\n<br />\n死者家屬事後向涉事旅行社交涉，惟負責人表示，呂翁死於火車，又非購物過程中，屬於自然死亡，並表示事件已交由常州市旅遊局處理。目前，當局已介入調查，老翁家人表明將通過法律途徑向涉事旅行社追討賠償。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180711/photo/bkn-20180711020011994-0711_00822_001_04p.jpg?20180711092044\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180711%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180711020011994-0711_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20180711092044&h=5344b613&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">呂翁早前的體檢報告。（互聯網）</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180711/bkn-20180711020011994-0711_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180711%2Fbkn-20180711020011994-0711_00822_001.html&d=voP7tq0CdGeXI%2FGEQLZGc7DFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=368d15c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180711/bkn-20180711020011994-0711_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n唔買嘢?玩撚死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e563e06685792dfce7cdbd106961c59ea51c026","tid":737738,"uid":8410,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T04:57:53.000Z","msg":"明知去呢d 旅行玩死自己<br />\n<br />\nPs. 中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec11c86bd8b26f5e0eb8f0fff9493525404ff0d","tid":737738,"uid":42188,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:00:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死者家屬事後向涉事旅行社交涉，惟負責人表示，呂翁死於火車，又非購物過程中，屬於自然死亡</blockquote>符合國情"},{"pid":"54006cc6dd3b886d3a925eb9ddc91706655e2b27","tid":737738,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:01:17.000Z","msg":"抵撚死 唔買野落黎做乜撚?<br />\n污染環境?<br />\n<br />\n正宗俾天收"},{"pid":"4a495995a6d933a6062ab37bf8a4d5134145f1e5","tid":737738,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:03:58.000Z","msg":"購物天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dcde7fbdb4fbe2d19329719bcc3be4fb43e94d","tid":737738,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:04:18.000Z","msg":"好在唔係死係香港 又要幫手醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad92de32ff8636ce5abfce5593bfdbe06c0c4cba","tid":737738,"uid":693,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:06:31.000Z","msg":"香港太危險, 千祁唔好黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a6d64bd2315bc2c6b85c40c640993fe928f60d","tid":737738,"uid":36441,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:17:08.000Z","msg":"係要貪平 咁多年都學唔精"},{"pid":"2cb6ecf9b4cfcae72fc6b2bd50651eb10c602ce4","tid":737738,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":1,